{"type":"step-attempt","step":"cross-boundary-invariants","sessionId":"6b450929-f29e-4627-86bb-b8ea39a4ec2c","outcome":{"verdict":"approved","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/bite-evidence-forward/cross-boundary-invariants-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"approved":true,"findings":[{"severity":"medium","resolution":"fixable","file":"src/core/runtime/local.ts","title":"verification.commands 設定時に forward 型 job でも無条件 strategy-deferred","rationale":"config.verification.commands が設定されているプロジェクトでは runTestsAtCommit が常に unavailable を返し、forward 型 job であっても gate が strategy-deferred になる。BiteEvidence レコードが一切生成されず、acceptance criterion「forward job でゲートが BiteEvidence を branch-borne に記録する」が無言でスキップされる。design の Open Questions に言及はあるが acceptance criteria に例外記述がなく、この経路のテストカバレッジも存在しない。","line":902},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"src/core/step/commit-orchestrator.ts","title":"conformance re-loop 時に captureHeadSha が null を返すと旧 biteEvidence が state に残留","rationale":"commitSuccess の biteEvidence 更新条件は completion.biteEvidence.length > 0 のみ。re-loop 中 captureHeadSha が null を返すと candidateOid=null → strategy-deferred → records:[] → 条件を満たさず旧レコードが残る。確率は極低（commitAndPush 成功後 git rev-parse HEAD が失敗する場合のみ）。機能的退行はないが state 上の evidence が旧 candidate を指したままになる。","line":336},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"src/core/step/bite-evidence/step.ts","title":"reads() に events.jsonl が未宣言","rationale":"BiteEvidenceStep.run() は tamper check のために events.jsonl を読むが reads() に宣言されていない。実行時影響はない（不在時は inconclusive にフォールバック）が、lineage graph の inputs が不完全になり artifact 観測性に欠ける。","line":108}],"observations":[{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/pipeline/reverification.ts","title":"IMPL_CODE_MUTATOR_STEPS に bite-evidence が含まれない — 意図通り","rationale":"bite-evidence は CLI step でコード変更なし。codeChangedSinceLastVerification の比較対象外であり reverification path への副作用はない。conformance → approved → verification (when) の条件は implementer の endedAt と verification の endedAt の比較で正しく動作する。"},{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/pipeline/compose-reviewers.ts","title":"composeReviewerDescriptor は implementer→bite-evidence edge に干渉しない","rationale":"custom reviewer chain は code-review 以降に挿入される。implementer → bite-evidence の遷移は STANDARD_TRANSITIONS に固定されており compose 操作の影響外。"},{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/runtime/managed.ts","title":"managed runtime: 両ポートが unavailable → strategy-deferred で一貫","rationale":"listCommitChangedFiles / runTestsAtCommit ともに unavailable を返す。digestArtifacts は null hash → inconclusive → ゲートは runtime capability check で strategy-deferred に至る。fail-open だが managed runtime の structural limitation として design D4 で明文化済み。"}]},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0,"addedTurns":{"reportRetry":0,"postWork":0,"outputRepair":0}},"startedAt":"2026-07-16T15:41:57.286Z","endedAt":"2026-07-16T15:53:01.811Z"}
{"type":"step-attempt","step":"scale-tolerance","sessionId":"cb7049af-b6b1-472c-a325-5d40b67172a8","outcome":{"verdict":"approved","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/bite-evidence-forward/scale-tolerance-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"approved":true,"findings":[],"observations":[{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/runtime/local.ts","title":"Sequential per-file subprocess spawning: 2N bun test invocations","rationale":"runTestsAtCommit spawns `bun test <file>` for each materialized test file sequentially, then repeats at the candidate OID — 2N subprocess invocations where N = files added by the test-materialize commit. N is bounded per commit (not a monotonically growing cross-job collection), so this is not a scale-tolerance violation. However, for a commit materializing many test files, bun startup overhead compounds linearly. A future optimization can batch: `bun test <file1> <file2> ...` reduces to 2 spawns while preserving per-file pass/fail via test-reporter output. Not a merge blocker.","line":909}]},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0,"addedTurns":{"reportRetry":0,"postWork":0,"outputRepair":0}},"startedAt":"2026-07-16T15:41:57.286Z","endedAt":"2026-07-16T15:45:07.939Z"}
